                be simplified to <m>\sfrac{9}{7}=e^{0.08t}</m>.  We can solve this 
                using our graphing calculator as shown below -- this gives that <m>t\approx 3.14</m>. 
                So it would take just over <m>3</m> years for our account to reach <m>\</m>9,000$.

                <image>
